text: Florent Maree (born 17 November 1980) is a French gymnast. He competed at the 2000 Summer Olympics and the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:People from Saint-Louis, Réunion
